title: 3 Large Bedrooms, Large Living Room, Kitchen/dining/6401 Rialto Blvd
posting_body: Newer Over-sized 3 Bedroom First Floor Apartment
3 Large Bedrooms, Large Living Room, Kitchen/dining area and bathroom with full-size bathtub.

Off Street parking for 1 car included.
2nd car parking considered for an extra fee
